Detailed Description

template<>
class Givaro::ZpzDom< Integer >

This class implement the standard arithmetic with Modulo Elements.

  • The representation of an integer a in Zpz is the value a % p
Examples:

examples/FiniteField/all_field.C, examples/FiniteField/ff_arith.C, examples/FiniteField/kronecker.C, examples/Integer/iexponentiation.C, and examples/Polynomial/PolynomialCRT.C.
